                    by completing the Photograpgher Form found through this link 
                    or through the "Getting Involved" page.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    How can I sign up to volunteer?
                    <span class="faq-arrow">&#9654;</span>
                </button>
