                    <span class="faq-arrow">&#9654;</span>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    You can apply to perform at AubFest by sending us
                    an email at aubfest@gmail.com or by following the 
                    link on the "Getting Involved" page.
                </div>
            </div>
